'''馬特·格利梅斯'''（{{lang-en|Matt Grimes}}；{{bd|1995年|7月15日}}）是一位[[英格蘭|英格蘭]]足球運動員，在場上的位置是中場。他現在效力於[[英冠|英冠]]球隊[[斯旺西城足球俱樂部|斯旺西]]<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/30632655 |title=Matt Grimes: Swansea City sign midfielder from Exeter City |publisher=BBC Sport |date=2 January 2015 |accessdate=2 January 2015 |archive-date=2015-08-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150829223819/http://www.bbc.co.uk/sport/0/football/30632655 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。他也代表英格蘭國青隊參賽<ref>{{cite web|title=Aidy Boothroyd names U20 squad to face Romania|url=http://www.thefa.com/news/england/development/2014/aug/boothroyd-names-his-first-u20-squad|publisher=[[The_FA|The FA]]|accessdate=28 August 2014|date=28 August 2014|archive-date=2014-09-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140903133929/http://www.thefa.com/news/england/development/2014/aug/boothroyd-names-his-first-u20-squad|dead-url=no}}</ref>。格利梅斯的職業生涯開始於[[埃克塞特城足球俱乐部|埃克塞特城]]<ref>{{cite web|title=Two scholars handed contracts with Exeter|url=http://www.exetercityfc.co.uk/news/article/pym-and-grimes-given-pro-deals-753303.aspx|work=exetercityfc.co.uk|accessdate=18 August 2013|archive-date=2016-08-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160825220910/http://www.exetercityfc.co.uk/news/article/pym-and-grimes-given-pro-deals-753303.aspx|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在2013-14賽季，他曾是埃克塞特城的年度選手。

